## Source: ossf-package-analysis (cae1528814e2419343da0b29f82d02fd957543fb2cccf0a367af9c18d1421d9b)
The OpenSSF Package Analysis project identified 'gatsby-starter-gitlab' @ 1.0.0 (npm) as malicious.

It is considered malicious because:

- The package communicates with a domain associated with malicious activity.

- The package executes one or more commands associated with malicious behavior.
